imdb.plot outline: The current Romanian version of the The Farm reality television show. The series premiered on March 9, 2015 on Pro TV. The show is about a group of celebrities living together twenty-four hours a day in a Farm, isolated from the outside world (primarily from mass media, such as newspapers, telephones, television and the internet) while having all their steps followed by cameras around-the-clock, with no privacy for three months. The contestants compete for the chance to win the grand prize by avoiding weekly eviction, until the last celebrity remains at the end of the season that can claim the grand prize. The show is presented by Iulia Vântur.
imdb.title: Ferma Vedetelor
plot: 13 spoiled celebrities are put to live at the farm in the conditions like 100 years ago. No electricity, no comfort, limited amount of food. Will they show their true faces?

The current Romanian version of the The Farm reality television show. The series premiered on March 9, 2015 on Pro TV. The show is about a group of celebrities living together twenty-four hours a day in a Farm, isolated from the outside world (primarily from mass media, such as newspapers, telephones, television and the internet) while having all their steps followed by cameras around-the-clock, with no privacy for three months. The contestants compete for the chance to win the grand prize by avoiding weekly eviction, until the last celebrity remains at the end of the season that can claim the grand prize. The show is presented by Iulia Vântur.::Cosmin Agafitei
